text: Amblymora australica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1948. It is known from Australia.BioLib.cz - Amblymora australica. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Amblymora Category:Beetles described in 1948
title: Amblymora australica
